                                                    Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus
                                                    viverra turpis.
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </li>
                                        <!-- Nested media object -->
                                        <li class="media">
                                            <div class="media-left">
                                                <a href="#">
                                                    <img class="media-object" alt="64x64" src="~/assets/images/team/team-member-3.jpg" data-holder-rendered="true" />
                                                </a>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="media-body">
                                                <h4 class="media-heading text-primary">Jihn Doe <span class="pull-right small text-muted"><i>3h ago</i></span></h4>
                                                <p>
                                                    Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla.
                                                    Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin commodo.
                                                    Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus
                                                    viverra turpis.
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </li>
